                            is licensed <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/">CC BY NC SA 4.0</a>.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
        </div>

        </section>
        <!-- <figure class="image is-16by9">
            <img src="https://michaelhyatt.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/updated-whack-a-mole-1920x1080.jpg">
        </figure> -->


    </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>